  • java.lang.Object
    • overwatch.controllers.TabController<T>

    public abstract class TabController<T extends java.awt.Component>
extends java.lang.Object
    Specifies a common external interface for tab controllers. Used in the Gui class for registering controllers to receive tab change notifications.
